  "texts": [
    "E. Evaluation SettingsWe report on our evaluation settings for RQ1.",
    "We note that RQ2 was based on our interview survey, and all the relevant details have been discussed above.",
    "RQ1 Evaluation.",
    "For answering RQ1, in the prompt generation step of RAGTAG, we experiment with two different settings -zero-shot (ZS) and few-shot (FS) prompting.",
    "For zero-shot prompting, we exclude the example TS (in Fig. 4), its description or any reference to the example TS from the prompt sent to the retrieval and the test case generation stages."
